1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 36=

3
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:18,760
You're with the Embroidered Guard?

4
00:00:19,120 --> 00:00:19,800
Yes.

5
00:00:22,559 --> 00:00:23,359
Vice Minister Zhou!

6
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:25,239
These charges are fabricated!

7
00:00:25,239 --> 00:00:28,879
Mao Buyu is colluding
with the Sacred Hand Sect to frame me!

8
00:00:29,079 --> 00:00:30,199
What about my father?

9
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:32,000
And Yunchang's father?

10
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:33,920
Were their deaths a setup too?

11
00:00:35,079 --> 00:00:37,520
Mao Jixian and Chu Xiangshan

12
00:00:38,159 --> 00:00:39,679
have nothing to do with me!

13
00:00:43,159 --> 00:00:43,920
Vice Minister.

14
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,640
And what is this?

15
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:55,039
This is what my father bit off

16
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:57,039
from his sleeve during the struggle,

17
00:00:57,560 --> 00:01:00,560
right as this man was killing him.

18
00:01:02,575 --> 00:01:04,640
Come. Try my new tea.

19
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,760
Thank you, Commissioner.

20
00:01:13,362 --> 00:01:14,241
Excellent tea.

21
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:19,840
Good.

22
00:01:22,159 --> 00:01:22,959
Commissioner...

23
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,840
You...

24
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,159
Jixian.

25
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,760
It's all right.

26
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,760
It will all be over soon.

27
00:01:52,250 --> 00:01:53,390
You think this scrap of cloth

28
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,560
proves it was mine?

29
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:01,560
Then take a look at this.

30
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,000
This gown

31
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,239
was found hidden in your wardrobe.

32
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:08,000
You were so sure
no one would suspect you

33
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:09,840
that you didn't even bother

34
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,719
to get rid of the evidence.

35
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,439
You're a monster.

36
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,319
So you really did kill my brother.

37
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,199
That's right.

38
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:21,039
And Mr. Chu was ambushed
and killed by him, too.

39
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:23,800
He even staged the entire crime scene.

40
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,199
You thought

41
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:30,360
that using the Nine-Flower Toxin
made you untouchable.

42
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,560
But you underestimated
Anran's skills as a coroner.

43
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:47,639
Nine-Flower Toxin...

44
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:51,319
That fool Xu Anran.

45
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:53,879
I should have silenced him long ago.

46
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:55,599
So you admit it?

47
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:59,439
When exactly did you
start plotting against me?

48
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:00,919
The moment Anran found

49
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:02,400
the truth behind my father's death.

50
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,280
I've been investigating you ever since.

51
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,120
I had Gao Shun dig through the archives.

52
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,639
Three years ago,

53
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,479
the plot to outlaw the Sacred Hand Sect

54
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:11,120
was your doing.

55
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,759
I traveled to Xichuan

56
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:14,240
to find Dongfang Bai

57
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:16,120
to uncover the rest of the truth.

58
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,319
When Chang appeared at the wedding,

59
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:20,759
I followed her here.

60
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,919
We traded what we knew,

61
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:24,680
and that's when the real mastermind

62
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,960
was finally exposed.

63
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:28,159
So, we beat you at your own game.

64
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:29,120
We faked our capture

65
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:31,520
to use Vice Minister Zhou as a witness

66
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,759
and expose your true color.

67
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,080
Luo Shixun,

68
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:36,159
you're meticulous.

69
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,439
No matter what evidence
we brought forward,

70
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:40,080
you could've buried it.

71
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,520
The only way to win

72
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,919
was to wait for your confession

73
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:46,919
when you get cocky.

74
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,800
I spent my life
thinking I was three steps ahead,

75
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,280
only to be outplayed
by a couple of children.

76
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,199
So be it!

77
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,159
Ms. Luo!

78
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,199
The Commissioner is in trouble.

79
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:10,960
Give the order!

80
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:12,759
Wushuang,

81
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,680
think carefully before you act.

82
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,919
Don't do anything reckless

83
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:16,800
and get involved.

84
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,600
Black-Clad Secret Guards!

85
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:20,800
Drop your weapons!

86
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,439
The Commissioner hand-picked us himself.

87
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,800
We will never betray him!

88
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:28,639
How dare you!

89
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:44,759
Call for backup, now!

90
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,360
Or do you want him to kill us all?

91
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,040
Get in here and seize the traitor!

92
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:50,399
Go!

93
00:04:50,399 --> 00:04:51,160
(Meditation Hall)
Yes, sir!

94
00:05:07,319 --> 00:05:07,920
Curse you...

95
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:11,987
Luo Shixun is guilty
of murder and conspiracy.

96
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,439
(Token)
Take him down!

97
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,680
Let's go.

98
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,920
I want him found and brought back alive!

99
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:39,920
And don't let Chu Yunchang escape!

100
00:05:46,487 --> 00:05:50,720
(Ministry of Justice)

101
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:54,160
By the grace of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees.

102
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:57,120
Luo Shixun, former Commissioner
of the Gate Bureau,

103
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:59,959
is guilty of
fabricating charges and murder.

104
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:02,759
By illicitly possessing the Sacred Token
with treacherous intent,

105
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:05,680
his crimes are absolute
and beyond pardon.

106
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:08,199
Following the council
of the Three Judiciaries

107
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:09,759
and the Cabinet's approval,

108
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:13,920
Luo Shixun is hereby stripped
of his rank as Commissioner.

109
00:06:13,930 --> 00:06:15,690
An empire-wide warrant
is issued for his arrest.

110
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:19,240
Yue Lun is appointed
Acting Commissioner of the Gate Bureau.

111
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:22,040
Mao Buyu,
formerly Deputy of the Arrest Corps,

112
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,970
is in truth a Commander
of the Embroidered Guard

113
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,240
acting on Imperial orders.

114
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:28,519
He is hereby reinstated to his post

115
00:06:28,730 --> 00:06:30,120
at the Northern Constabulary Office.

116
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:31,759
By Imperial Command.

117
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:33,600
- We live to serve!
- We live to serve!

118
00:06:33,612 --> 00:06:36,475
(Integrity and Justice)

119
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,000
Congrats, Yu!

120
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,000
- Well done, Commander.
- Congratulations!

121
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,920
You deserve it, Yu.

122
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,399
Don't forget us when you're at the top.

123
00:06:42,399 --> 00:06:43,680
Yeah, show us the ropes!

124
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,890
Help us become as great as you.

125
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:46,680
All right. Thank you, everyone.

126
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,240
Dinner is on me next time.

127
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,639
You're all dismissed for today.

128
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,160
Understood!

129
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,519
- Thanks, Yu!
- See you around!

130
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,480
Take care.

131
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:57,839
Master!

132
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:01,879
Master!

133
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,920
Is that the Flying Fish Robe?

134
00:07:06,439 --> 00:07:07,839
It looks incredible.

135
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:09,120
Is that real gold thread?

136
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:11,600
Let me try it on sometime.

137
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,800
You little brat.

138
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:48,439
(Father.)

139
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:51,120
(I hope your spirit is watching over us.)

140
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:55,399
(The Mao family can finally
hold our heads high again.)

141
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:16,920
What do you want?

142
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,319
Get out of my way.

143
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,759
What are you trying to pull, Dong?

144
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,519
I said move.

145
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:25,879
Are you deaf?

146
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:29,550
When my grandfather was here,

147
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,519
you would've shown some manners.

148
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:39,200
You know Luo Shixun is gone, don't you?

149
00:08:40,399 --> 00:08:41,600
Your grandfather is a fugitive.

150
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:44,360
And you've been demoted
to a common constable.

151
00:08:44,759 --> 00:08:46,080
The Gate Bureau

152
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:48,240
is no longer the Luo family's kingdom.

153
00:08:48,559 --> 00:08:49,279
Now,

154
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,600
get out of my way.

155
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:52,679
Or else...

156
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:53,440
Or else what?

157
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,279
- Commander!
- Commander!

158
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,679
Commander!

159
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,820
If I ever catch you harassing her again,

160
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:02,960
you'll be sorry.

161
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:03,799
Get out!

162
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,799
Yes, sir!

163
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:05,559
Let's go.

164
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:06,919
- Move!
- Yes.

165
00:09:11,799 --> 00:09:12,559
Are you all right?

166
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:15,559
It's a fickle world we live in.

167
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,679
Don't let those cowards get to you.

168
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,240
Thank you, Commander Mao.

169
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,639
Wushuang...

170
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,200
Your grandfather is his own man.

171
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:32,240
You're not him.

172
00:09:32,662 --> 00:09:34,090
As long as your conscience is clear,

173
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,360
you need not fear them.

174
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,500
My grandfather murdered your father.

175
00:09:42,559 --> 00:09:43,879
Do you really not hold a grudge?

176
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:13,639
Anran.

177
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,679
There's something
I still don't understand.

178
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,399
What is it?

179
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:23,320
Why would Luo Shixun murder my father?

180
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,039
A moment, Commander.

181
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,080
Director Liu.

182
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,190
Are you here to mock me too?

183
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,320
Not at all.

184
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:47,720
I'm here on orders
to collect the Sacred Token.

185
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:50,879
You want the Sacred Token?

186
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:51,919
Not me.

187
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,879
The Minister of Justice requested it.

188
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,240
Then follow me.

189
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,990
By the way, Director Liu,

190
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,600
I'll need you to sign a receipt for this.

191
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,200
Of course.

192
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:00,600
I won't take up any more of your time.

193
00:12:01,039 --> 00:12:02,840
I must get this
to the Ministry of Justice

194
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:04,080
to have it stored.

195
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:14,159
Director Liu?

196
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,600
It's nothing.

197
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:46,799
Who's there?

198
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:49,679
Shuang.

199
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:59,525
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

200
00:12:59,563 --> 00:13:02,438
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

201
00:13:02,938 --> 00:13:08,656
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

202
00:13:09,838 --> 00:13:13,158
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

203
00:13:13,288 --> 00:13:16,208
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

204
00:13:17,376 --> 00:13:22,616
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

205
00:13:23,838 --> 00:13:26,231
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

206
00:13:26,231 --> 00:13:29,881
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

207
00:13:29,950 --> 00:13:33,440
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

208
00:13:33,538 --> 00:13:36,513
♪To the ends of time♪

209
00:13:36,513 --> 00:13:39,888
♪The moon traces your face♪

210
00:13:40,075 --> 00:13:43,663
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

211
00:13:43,663 --> 00:13:49,903
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

212
00:13:50,238 --> 00:13:53,453
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

213
00:13:53,738 --> 00:13:57,276
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

214
00:13:57,563 --> 00:14:00,588
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

215
00:14:00,588 --> 00:14:03,688
♪On our way to forever♪

216
00:14:03,688 --> 00:14:07,538
♪The moon traces your face♪

217
00:14:07,538 --> 00:14:10,898
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

218
00:14:11,088 --> 00:14:17,048
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

219
00:14:18,125 --> 00:14:27,765
♪Just to be with you♪
